name: Tacoma Washington
description:
This trip was a special trip made with my brother and I to celebrate his graduation from high school - 2003 - we watched the start of the war together while sharing a beer - strange and surreal to watch the "shock and awe" happening - this place is the amazing glass blowing museum of Tacoma Washington - installation piece done by Chihuly
